<section id="pop" class="info">
    <div class="title">
        <h3 id="pd-bold-italic">POP ART</h3>
        <p class="left" id="os-bold">Pop Art emerged in the UK and in the US as a reaction to post war consumer
            culture. It took inspiration from popular
            culture like comic books, television and advertising, and artists represented everyday objects in their
            art. Pop art
            challenged the view on fine art by incorporating imagery from popular culture. The use of bold colors
            and collages is
            what makes it so recognizable today.</p>
    </div>
    <div>
        <h1 class="dates" id="limelight">1950s-1960s</h1>
    </div>
</section>

